OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers at first but soon becoming dry
OL,7,Fovernight with clear periods, although
OL,8,Fhigh level cloud increasing later.
OL,9,FWinds easing with some patchy ground
OL,10,Ffrost possible by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FChilly start, then bright
OL,13,Fspells through the morning but cloud
OL,14,Fthickens through the afternoon,
OL,15,Fperhaps bringing some patchy light
OL,16,Frain eastwards later. Becoming
OL,17,Fbreezier by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
