OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand strong winds early Saturday,
OL,7,Ffollowed by sunshine and blustery
OL,8,Fshowers into Sunday. Feeling rather
OL,9,Fcool at times. Monday, fewer showers
OL,10,Fand lighter winds. Temperatures mostly
OL,11,Faround average.
